    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to Scour Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>Scour</application> is an SVG (Scalable Vector Graphics)
        optimizer/cleaner that reduces their size by optimizing structure and
        removing unnecessary data.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

